{"tid":390341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港人爭住睇！】《戰狼II》早場銷售反應踴躍","createTime":"2017-09-07T04:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:13:07.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d1712001850d6da0f896c24b49197cf778eb75","tid":390341,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57177745&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57177745%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170906&d=sO0Px8KvEZm8glN2KaOhaf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3e50e8b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57177745%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170906&h=a25209e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57177745&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170906</a><br />\n<br />\n【香港人爭住睇！】主旋律電影《戰狼II》早上場次「包場式」見紅<br />\n即時娛樂 <br />\n2017-09-06 22:30:11 HKT<br />\n<br />\n由吳京做主角嘅《戰狼II》，早前喺大陸上畫，喺事前一片唱衰嘅情況下，上映42日，累計票房超過55.8億人民幣，登上中國史上最高票房電影，並且打入年度全球票房十大電影之一，部戲o依家仲上緊，同時更擠身史上全球最高電影票房首100位，創造咗「中國電影的神話」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然《戰狼II》喺大陸票房大收，但係睇返香港嘅售票情況就似乎唔係太踴躍，好多場次都只係有少量座位賣出，但係唔知係唔係因為早場票價比較平嘅關係，有唔少地區戲院嘅早場寧寧舍舍有幾排座位全滿，特別係喺元朗嘅戲院，連續兩日早場已售嘅座位有九成相似，之但係呢類「主旋律」電影，喺大陸上映後都有唔少公司或機構會包場叫員工睇，到底今次喺香港上映係包場定咁啱就真係冇人知喇。<br />\n<br />\n而《戰狼2》喺電影評分網站imdb嘅分數都唔弱，10分滿分，佢有6.8分(2015年嘅《戰狼》就有5.4分)，有份評分嘅，男性有1,060人，女性只係有244人。俾10分心心眼滿分嘅，佔36.6%，俾1分嘅佔9.8%，根據imdb個分析，俾10分滿分嘅，其中兩個係聲稱未夠18歲嘅女性。"},{"pid":"4e2bb7b8fbc46a462162afe47ce98a9ea691a447","tid":390341,"uid":10064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"早場既年齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b28170da30dcaeab4b9750cbec4ce14ce1a4f69","tid":390341,"uid":37735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"看的永世做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649a9684e299f39e3a4465387f617eef4da50ac6","tid":390341,"uid":48,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"元朗戲院細到仆街 梗係爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5406d477b109969c39adfee34e36166e8916190","tid":390341,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"但晚上好多得－場<br />\nwhy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09696b0601a482f489f0256ff10d0395a3d7f62","tid":390341,"uid":761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:01:30.000Z","msg":"廢老🤷🏿&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"234b721db1dcd49a5b47fe0ed8ad4f34af018b01","tid":390341,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"呢套野咩料"},{"pid":"1fc67dbd6ac2ce02977faead2aa8b4816b42a8da","tid":390341,"uid":24140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套野咩料</blockquote><br />\n支那國既打飛機電影"},{"pid":"d66f8c01a96f80a271478d049b5b96b29a1fa161","tid":390341,"uid":3117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"請左幾多人做媒"},{"pid":"755da6b51a93fab1cb7c9df12562386598d7ed57","tid":390341,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"支那收二三十億,掉返兩三億去香港買票房"},{"pid":"f189a3efa3a573a927db3061fe41d85ad1f75e1b","tid":390341,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那收二三十億,掉返兩三億去香港買票房</blockquote><br />\n用之前解國大業個招 成場爆滿 點知入面全吉位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb83091fa495ed692e52d2f0348388672e743c4","tid":390341,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:10:17.000Z",